    <item>
      <title>Landlord-Tenant Communication Tool</title>
      <link>https://jdaumeyer.com/posts/capstone/</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Developed in collaboration with JusticeTech at the Moritz College of Law, with a cross discipline team. This tool beutifies the language used by tenants when communicating issues to their landlords, in order to prevent angry messages or errors of speech.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I was responsible for the frontend design of the app, ensuring that the form flowed nicely and the site was accessible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Skills &amp; Tools Used&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;display:flex;flex: 0 1 row;list-style: none;padding:0;gap: 1em;margin-top:0;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li&gt; React &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt; Agile &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt; Git &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt; Typescript &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt; Trello &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt; Figma &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

